{"tid":1470858,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[心理戰] 贏 人 必 須 先 贏 自 己","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:27:15.000Z","uid":290721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"963834274ace38a778761f39ee4e502b811d064f","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"首先，不論你係勇武派定和理非<br />\n同自己講聲：呢段日子(自己個名)已經做得好好，辛苦哂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n持續左兩個幾月既抗爭，你要面對無能既政權、唔公義既事情、眼見手足被捕被打卻無能為力，但仍然選擇繼續抗爭，真係好唔容易！你地真係叻到痴左線啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：我係一名由69到宜家同大家一齊抗爭亦食過幾次催淚彈既和理非。無論點定必同大家抗爭到底，不撤不散，不割蓆，不分化，不篤灰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講番正題：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每場抗爭贏人都必須先贏自己！</span></span></strong>我地一日打敗唔到自己既心理弱點，我地任何抗爭都只係會失敗收場！<br />\n<br />\n以下係我認為造成失敗既陷阱：<br />\n1. 對於失敗既諗法<br />\n香港既教育制度重視結果，忽略過程，令我地覺得做錯一件事就等同失敗。<br />\n尋晚好多人都話「我地尋晚輸左啊，好灰，唔知之後可以點。」<br />\n大佬，你當我地宜家係去緊一個無人去過既地方，條路無人行過，行錯撞板係一定會。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行錯路唔代表你會去唔到目的地，只係話比你知此路不通。</span></strong><br />\n你可以做既係：係地圖畫番個交叉，下次唔好再行。無必要指責帶頭行呢條路既人，團隊每一個都有責任，加上條路無人行過，唔行係唔會知呢條係死路！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"> &quot;Failure is not when we make mistakes. Failure is when we stop trying.&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 成功錯覺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鼓吹階段性既勝利令你產生一切順利既陷阱</span></strong>。驕傲同自滿會令我地掉以輕心，看自己比別人強，推我地去到危險之地，係抗爭者既絆腳石。<br />\n因此我地必須時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<br />\n3. 搞錯目標<br />\n如果我地設立過多目標既時候，人係會傾向去做難易度最低既目標而唔係最重要既目標。先去完成難易度最低既目標只<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">會令你忽略當下最重要既事同消耗你大部份既時間去爭取較唔重要既目標</span></strong>！<br />\n我唔係反對機場和你飛以眼還眼，亦都唔係指以眼還眼唔重要，但大家唔好失焦。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請記住最重要既事係五大訴求！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n4. 一遇到挫折就自暴自棄<br />\n抗爭最忌諱就係陷入自暴自棄既心態之中。自暴自棄既心態係用偶然既一次錯誤成為你之後破例其他事既藉口。<br />\n正確既心態應該係我<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今次唔小心破例左一次，我之後要更堅守我既目標先岩啊！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 用我最中意既quote鼓勵大家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;There are no hopeless circumstances, just hopeless people!&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n半杯水既比喻，一個玻璃杯，裡面有半杯水。<br />\n有人見到半空，有人見到半滿。<br />\n重點係你既心態。<br />\nSing Hallelujah To The Lord!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5633e5623c39a00b8d70f71f3a7fa62a68cffd","tid":1470858,"uid":296264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96cde6040bd6059796d5f991f8ad8072264d5bfb","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2bf36cc90df10498d638cc95207e4dfcf68c19","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11e665d5c5e46f46729085e905e650d5335d467","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ab58011f680174ebfddcd69668295a22d637a3","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c626a0d35572e613813e611220015ac724757e9e","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b18d146486b5c5600e0d837a2f0159b1995799","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a81e70fa89e39c7b21f8524a235c5a9a352c9dd","tid":1470858,"uid":104145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6777eee891d39563e574b41e41d5ec4f202d698","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07539c91e8e78f8abd4cbde295e0988bbf5748c","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0555ba40ba85bff8b1d618288e5fb49fb5caf2","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcee0c8a5d2b99f169c804439de302baa9f5aed0","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1097529986dbf06144288c3aa2ae0d31cb770d6a","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c2b95f13c8d38ae4d0e3a227be6102acefe30bd8","tid":1470858,"uid":290721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}